    "ADT (admit/discharge/transfer) feeds to downstream systems",
    "Lab results (ORU^R01) from LIS to EHR",
    "Radiology order (ORM^O01) and result (ORU^R01) workflow",
    "Health information exchange (HIE) message routing"
  ],
